Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2
! const values for parameter: iDet2D DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE = 1 DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED = 2
! const values for parameter: iFieldType FIELDTYPE_MAJOR = 1 FIELDTYPE_LITTLE = 2
! const values for parameter: iFieldSurface FIELDSURFACE_DIRT = 1 FIELDSURFACE_GRASS = 2
if iFieldSurface = FIELDSURFACE_DIRT then court_mat = 33 if iFieldSurface = FIELDSURFACE_GRASS then court_mat = 30
if field=0 then bac=0 outfield=0 otffen=0 endif
fv=0.05 parameters zzyzx=fv vv=0.1
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.` values{2} "iFieldType" FIELDTYPE_MAJOR, `Главная Лига`, FIELDTYPE_LITTLE, `Детская Лига`
values{2} "iDet2D" DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE, `Простой`
values{2} "iFieldSurface" FIELDSURFACE_DIRT, `Грунт`, FIELDSURFACE_GRASS, `Трава`
if iFieldSurface = FIELDSURFACE_DIRT then court_mat = 30
if otffen=0 then hideparameter "otf" if outfield=0 then hideparameter "otffen" if bac=0 then hideparameter "h" if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=4 if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=91 if turf_fill_pen=0 then parameters turf_fill_pen=91 if line_fill_pen=0 then parameters line_fill_pen=91
if gs_resol<3 then parameters gs_resol=3 If gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then lock "gs_resol"
if iFieldType = FIELDTYPE_MAJOR then parameters a=90' parameters b=90' lock "a" lock "b" endif
if iFieldType = FIELDTYPE_LITTLE then parameters a=60' parameters b=60' lock "a" lock "b" endif
Symbol.Comment: Поле для бейсбола различных размеров, дополнительно дальняя часть поля, ограждение и сетчатое ограждение сзади.
